purse. But when you buy the books (or at least send an
email to <a href="mailto:mde@saratbookhouse.com">my
distributor</a> with a request to buy), you are
sending <i>him</i> the valuable message that the books are in
demand.  He does not care about my dreams. Market demand (as
perceived by him in terms of cash) is his only motivation.</LI>
